      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Solid classic with plenty of charm and a nice entry point into vintage ownership. This is a fair-condition driver that presents respectably and has the kind of character that makes it enjoyable to own, but it\u2019s not a show car and does show age in both cosmetics and overall finish. A good fit for someone who wants a usable classic they can enjoy now and improve over time.",
