      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Affordable project car with plenty of potential for the right buyer. This one is in poor condition overall and will need mechanical and cosmetic work, with clear wear, age-related issues, and a rough presentation throughout. That said, it could be a worthwhile opportunity for someone looking for a fixer-upper, a budget entry point, or a parts car. Priced honestly for what it is and ready for its next chapter.",
