    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "A solid good-condition example that shows well and should make a very satisfying driver for someone who wants a clean, usable car without paying top money for a showpiece. It presents nicely overall, with the kind of normal age and use-related wear you would expect on a well-kept vehicle rather than a fully restored or near-new example. The body, paint, and interior are respectable and enjoyable as-is, and while it is not perfect, it has clearly been maintained well enough to remain attractive and practical. Buyers should expect a car that is honest, presentable, and ready to be enjoyed, with the minor flaws and cosmetic imperfections typical of a good driver-quality vehicle.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Older car in fair overall condition with the kind of age and wear you would expect from a driver-quality example. It appears presentable and largely complete, with enough going for it to enjoy as-is while improving over time, but it is not a mint or fully sorted show car. Expect visible cosmetic imperfections, an older interior, and the possibility of some mechanical or maintenance items needing attention as part of regular ownership. A solid candidate for someone looking for an affordable entry point into this model without paying top-tier money.",
      "price": 16900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
